<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="iddc708163-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee" identifier="/us/usc/t2/s21"><num value="21">§ 21.</num><heading> Oath of Senators</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The oath of office shall be administered by the President of the Senate to each Senator who shall be elected, previous to his taking his seat.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="iddc708164-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee">(R.S. § 28.)</sourceCredit>
